title: The Law of Action
itunes:title: The Law of Action
description:
Episode 160 - If you have not listened to Episode 159, you will want to listen to that episode first. That being said, this episode covers the next step in The Law of Attraction, the part that I believe The Secret leaves out, the part where you actually get off you butt and put in work. The universe rewards those who work and in this episode I explain the subject more in depth.
